data.title: Study of a “bloom” of the oil-rich alga Botryococcus braunii in the Darwin River Reservoir
data.meta_description: A “bloom” of the freshwater alga Botryococcus braunii Kützing appeared in the Darwin River Reservoir in 1976. At the time of algal sampling, the
